'''Keroselene''' is a highly volatile derivative during the steam distillation of [[coal-tar]]. It was discovered in 1861 by [[Joshua Merrill]]. It has been used as a local [[anaesthetic]].<ref>{{cite book|last1=Henry Munson Lyman|title=Artificial Anæsthesia and Anæsthetics (Volume 17 of Wood's library of standard medical authors)|date=1881|publisher=W. Wood|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xNEIAQAAIAAJ&dq=Keroselene&pg=PA226#v=onepage&q=Keroselene&f=false|accessdate=26 September 2015}}</ref>

