The '''Società Elettrica Sopracenerina''', or '''Electricity Company of Sopraceneri''', is a [[Switzerland|Swiss]] [[electricity supply]] company. It operates throughout the [[Sopraceneri]] region of the [[canton of Ticino]], and is headquartered in the [[Locarno|city of Locarno]]. It is part of the [[Alpiq Group]].<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.alpiq.com/about-alpiq/our-business/group-companies/alpiqsopracaneria.jsp | title = Power supplier in Ticino | publisher = Alpiq Group | accessdate = 2012-11-22}}</ref>

